        "EdgeChallengeManager configuration: excessStakeReceiver, stakeToken, stakeAmounts[], challengePeriodBlocks, assertionChain, oneStepProofEntry, layer-zero heights, NUM_BIGSTEP_LEVEL",
        "RollupCore protocol config state: chainId, confirmPeriodBlocks, baseStake, wasmModuleRoot, challengeManager, challengeGracePeriodBlocks, inbox/bridge/outbox/rollupEventInbox addresses, validatorWalletCreator, loserStakeEscrow, stakeToken, minimumAssertionPeriod, anyTrustFastConfirmer, validatorWhitelistDisabled",
