        "Assertion finality/confirmation status (_latestConfirmed, AssertionConfirmed events) as protocol trust/finality signal",
        "Edge confirmation status (EdgeStatus Confirmed) and confirmedRivals records impacting dispute outcomes",
        "Whitelist status (validatorWhitelistDisabled) affecting decentralization assumptions and trust model"
